title: Ravens-Rams MNF Recap, Did Lamar lock up MVP? Jared Goff concerns (Football 11/26)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Ryan Wilson, John Breech and Sean Wagner-McGough to recap the Ravens 45-6 victory over the Rams on Monday Night Football (1:15). The guys discuss another brilliant performance from Lamar Jackson and how he is currently transcending the NFL before analyzing Baltimore's chances if they meet New England again the in the postseason. The Pick Six Superfriends also take a look at the ugly effort from Los Angeles and how things have gone wrong for Sean McVay. Next, Andy Dalton is back as the Bengals starting quarterback as John Breech breaks down the move (29:15). Then, a lengthy conversation on QB uncertainty around the league, centered around Jared Goff and other teams that could be in bad spots at the position (42:00).
